title: Ilya Vakhrushev
text:
Ilya Olegovich Vakhrushev (; born 3 May 1989) is a former <a href="Russia">Russia</a>n professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a>er.
Club career.
He played in the <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> for <a href="FC%20Zvezda%20Irkutsk">FC Zvezda Irkutsk</a> in 2008.
He made his only appearance for the senior squad of <a href="FC%20Tom%20Tomsk">FC Tom Tomsk</a> on 15 July 2009 in a <a href="Russian%20Cup%20%28football%29">Russian Cup</a> game against <a href="FC%20Alania%20Vladikavkaz">FC Alania Vladikavkaz</a>.
